creator: Kalekik Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Offside is a free* social sports app. It provides you with a guided chat platform where you can discuss live matches with your friends. Also you will get live match updates so you don’t miss anything. Additionally, we also post non-money prediction questions at regular intervals, allowing you to compete with your friends and increase engagement with the match.

We provides sports fans with:
- Chat platform designed to simplify live sports discussion
- Prediction events to enhance the match viewing experience
- Live match updates ensure that fans don’t miss anything

Chat simplifies participating in multiple groups & individuals during a live match.

Non-money predictions enhance the match viewing experience by asking intriguing questions to engage you and your friends. There are weekly rewards based on points earned during that week from predictions.

Live match updates are built within the chat and provide ball-by-ball detailed coverage of the match.

The Game hub, which is unique to each match, is the heart of our platform, combining all of the features listed above into a single interface. During the game, the platform keeps the conversation going by sending users prediction questions, commentaries, and trivia.

*Data charges may apply. Contact your provider for details.
—
If you have any feedback or questions, please go to Offside > Homepage > Feedback or Offside > Profile > Feedback.

creator: Firkie Sports India Pvt. Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Dive into the ultimate cricketing experience with Offside, your one-stop destination for all things cricket! We offer you everything from IPL to Asia Cup and ODI Cricket World Cup updates, discussions, handpicked cricket content, engaging quizzes, contests, and much more.

We provide Cricket fans like you with the following:
👥 Communities for cricket fans to connect and share their passion for the sport
💬 Live match discussions and 24*7 cricket conversations with fellow fans
📝 Text/Audio cricket quizzes to test your knowledge and challenge your friends
🎯 Cricket contests/games like Reverse Fantasy to add a fun twist to the game
🔮 Cricket Predictions to capture the flow of match
📚 Curated cricket content to keep you updated with the latest news, insights, and facts
🏆 Weekly and monthly rewards from various free-to-play contests
🤝 Enjoy cricket together with your friends like never before

We enhance your experience around cricket with features like non-monetary predictions, Reverse Fantasy games, engaging quizzes, trivia, diverse cricket content and a vibrant community. Plus, our live match updates, complete with ball-by-ball coverage and in-depth player stats, ensure you stay in sync with the game you love.
—
Please go to Offside > Profile > Settings > Feedback if you have any feedback or questions in the app.
